intent.user_query: What are the products that are most frequently associated with service tickets marked as 'Urgent' (assuming such a status exists, if not default to 'Open')?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS NumberOfTickets FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.ServiceTickets st ON p.ProductID = st.ProductID WHERE st.Status = 'Open' GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY NumberOfTickets DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY NumberOfTickets DESC) <= 5;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS NumberOfTickets FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.ServiceTickets st ON p.ProductID = st.ProductID WHERE st.Status = 'Open' GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY NumberOfTickets DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY NumberOfTickets DESC) <= 5;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
